b. Provide adequate manpower to assist the BAC Secretariat; and
c. Instruct the Municipal Engineer to include in his letter request for inspection the duly accomplished and signed Checklist for technical evaluation of infrastructure projects, the progress accomplishment and the additional documentary requirements for final payments.

